caption: After visiting Eiffel tower  we usually walk on the other side of this seine, however, this time for a change, we ventured along the left bank, we literally stumbled onto this amazing floating barges of imitation islands, the piece de resistance, was sun lounge, at this stage we had walked for miles and these beds were a welcome relief for our tired feet, also the perfect place to have a picnic, what was surprising was no one was there using them, there were tourists everywhere but none here, as it turns out a secret garden area, only the locals know about.
